The package boost-odeint is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS numeric_odeint)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::numeric_odeint)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_odeint REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::numeric_odeint)
